<td class="contentheading" width="100%">
Вопрос - ответ. О торговле индульгенциями </td>
<td align="right" width="100%" class="buttonheading">
<a href="/index.php?view=article&amp;catid=110:2008-02-18-12-56-16&amp;id=1501:2009-03-23-07-51-38&amp;tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;layout=default&amp;page=" title="Печать" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','status=no,toolbar=no,scrollbars=yes,titlebar=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480,directories=no,location=no'); return false;" rel="nofollow"><img src="/images/M_images/printButton.png" alt="Печать"/></a> </td>
<td align="right" width="100%" class="buttonheading">
<a href="/index.php?option=com_mailto&amp;tmpl=component&amp;link=7d77653cc542a3e12417a047493ea16c9cce6302" title="E-mail" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','width=400,height=350,menubar=yes,resizable=yes'); return false;"><img src="/images/M_images/emailButton.png" alt="E-mail"/></a> </td>
</tr>
